        <section id="suggested-changes">
            <h2>Suggested Changes</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Ensure stories are personal and not made up by AI.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="risks">
            <h2>Risks and Mitigation</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Bias in presentation materials - Cross-validation for diverse perspectives.</li>
                <li>Privacy issues - Strip private information before processing.</li>
                <li>Fake stories - Maintain authenticity and human oversight.</li>
                <li>Accuracy concerns - Validate sources and AI outputs.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="policies">
            <h2>Policy Suggestions</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Pay royalties to providers of research and statistics.</li>
                <li>Limit AI usage to 30%, ensuring gradual migration.</li>
                <li>Keep humans in decision-making loops.</li>
                <li>Validate AI recommendations with human oversight.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="prompts">
            <h2>Prompts</h2>
            <h3>Visualize the Results</h3>
            <p>
                <strong>Description:</strong> Creates an image of what your solution to the need will look like by interactively asking questions about the purpose of the image.
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>Prompt:</strong> 
                "Create a visually striking image inspired by a persuasive speech, focusing on the key elements provided below. Answer the following questions to refine the image prompt for maximum impact:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Task:</strong> What is the primary goal of the image?</li>
                <li><strong>Context:</strong> What is the setting or backdrop?</li>
                <li><strong>Visual Elements:</strong> Are there specific elements or metaphors?</li>
                <li><strong>Persona:</strong> Who is the target audience?</li>
                <li><strong>Format:</strong> What format should the image take?</li>
                <li><strong>Tone:</strong> What is the emotional tone?</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
